user.en:
Write a USER.md profile file for a DevOps/SRE AI agent.
Agent: {{agentName}} | Role: {{agentRole}}
Team: {{scenarioName}}

Write 1 sentence describing the engineering lead or on-call manager this agent serves — their role, reliability expectations, and escalation preferences.

Output plain markdown text only. No JSON.

user.zh:
为 DevOps/SRE AI 智能体写一份 USER.md 画像文件。
智能体：{{agentName}} | 角色：{{agentRole}}
团队：{{scenarioName}}

写1句话描述该智能体服务的工程负责人或值班经理——其角色、可靠性期望和升级偏好。

仅输出纯 Markdown 文本，不要 JSON。

heartbeat.en:
Write a HEARTBEAT.md checklist for a DevOps/SRE AI agent.
Agent: {{agentName}} | Role: {{agentRole}}
Team: {{scenarioName}}

Output 5 recurring operational task checkboxes specific to this agent's on-call/SRE role.
Format: - [ ] task description

No headings, no other text.

heartbeat.zh:
